# My slides and demo code are in the repo this is linked to!

# Book an appointment, skip the line!

[Book here](https://slotted.co/sea-int-nodebotanist)

# Some of the tools I'll have handy

* [Oscilloscope \(DSO Nano\)](https://www.seeedstudio.com/dso-nano-v3-p-1358.html)
* [Digilent Analog Discovery 2](https://www.sparkfun.com/products/13929)
* [Bus Pirate](http://dangerousprototypes.com/docs/Bus_Pirate)
* AVR Programmer (regular and AVRTiny)
* Bluetooth LE traffic sniffer
* Travel router w/OpenWRT installed
* Kinoma create V2
* FTDI Cable
* Serial-to-ttl cable
* Soldering Iron & Setup
* Various tools and consumables

# See what I've been working on lately

I've [made my lab notebook public](https://t.co/cEAAJ2hiG3)!
